  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Abide, O dearest Jesus, Among us with Thy grace, That Satan may not harm us, Nor we to sin give place.",
    "v2": "Abide, O dear Redeemer, Among us with Thy Word, And thus now and hereafter True peace and joy afford.",
    "v3": "Abide with heav&#39;nly brightness Among us, precious Light; Thy truth direct, and keep us From error&#39;s gloomy night.",
    "v4": "Abide with richest blessings Among us, bounteous Lord; Let us in grace and wisdom Grow daily through Thy Word.",
    "v5": "Abide with Thy protection Among us, Lord, our Strength, Lest world and Satan fell us And overcome at length."
  },
